==发射和坠落==
萤火一号2009年6月完成正样并赴俄罗斯联合测试。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]2011年11月8日20:16（北京時間9日凌晨4:16）成功发射，但俄方探测器未能成功变轨，以至于未能脱离地球轨道。<ref name="BBC">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/rolling_news/2011/11/111109_rolling_china_mars_probe.shtml|title=中國首個火星探測器順利升空|agency=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2011-11-09|language=zh-hant|access-date=2011-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111112133758/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/rolling_news/2011/11/111109_rolling_china_mars_probe.shtml|archive-date=2011-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="xinhuanet">{{Cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2011-11/09/c_122252909.htm|title=中国首个火星探测器“萤火一号”顺利升空|publisher=[[新华网|新华网]]|date=2011-11-09|language=zh-hans|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110154934/http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2011-11/09/c_122252909.htm|archivedate=2011-11-10}}</ref><ref name="russianspaceweb">{{Cite web|url=http://www.russianspaceweb.com/phobos_grunt_scenario.html|title=Phobos-Grunt mission scenario|publisher=RussianSpaceWeb.com|accessdate=2011-11-08|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110231443/http://www.russianspaceweb.com/phobos_grunt_scenario.html|archive-date=2011-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AFP">{{Cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5g2TZ2yTAdpilqHKfBsYzrZZDv4JA?docId=CNG.b79c80941a75d4c1600f862c096035db.21|title=Russia aims for first conquest of Mars|author=Stuart Williams|agency=[[法新社|法新社]]|publisher=[[Google新闻|Google新闻]]|date=2011-11-07|language=en|access-date=2011-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111111141820/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5g2TZ2yTAdpilqHKfBsYzrZZDv4JA?docId=CNG.b79c80941a75d4c1600f862c096035db.21|archive-date=2011-11-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据[[俄新网|俄新网]]报道，[[俄罗斯联邦航天局|俄罗斯联邦航天局]]局长称，莫斯科时间2011年11月9日凌晨在[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]境内[[拜科努尔发射场|拜科努尔发射场]]发射、搭载有萤火一号火星探测器的福布斯－土壤探测器在与运载火箭分离后，未能按计划变轨，被困在距離地表206到340公里的太空中。[[俄羅斯聯邦太空局|俄羅斯聯邦太空局]]先後兩次搶救都未成功，有專家概算此衛星可能墜毀地球的時間和地點，尤其它載有12噸有毒燃料撞地球後可能引發的災難<ref>{{cite news|author=中广网|title=俄火星探测器未能按计划变轨 搭载有中国探测器|url=http://finance.ifeng.com/roll/20111109/5020665.shtml|publisher=凤凰网|date=2011-11-09|access-date=2011-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121218051915/http://finance.ifeng.com/roll/20111109/5020665.shtml|archive-date=2012-12-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://www2.cna.com.tw/ShowNews/Detail.aspx?pNewsID=201111120250&pType0=aCN&pTypeSel=0 搶救俄羅斯衛星 陸只有乾瞪眼 台北/中央社 2011/11/12 22:24] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113055353/http://www2.cna.com.tw/ShowNews/Detail.aspx?pNewsID=201111120250&pType0=aCN&pTypeSel=0 |date=2011-11-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=新京报|title=当心“毒卫星”来袭！|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2011-11/20/c_122307410.htm|publisher=新华网|date=2011-11-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425221016/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2011-11/20/c_122307410.htm|archivedate=2012-04-25}}</ref>。

该卫星部分碎片于2012年1月15日17时45分坠于太平洋海域，<ref name=ABCFinished>[http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/phobos-grunt-failed-russian-mars-probe-falls-earth/story?id=15366151 "Phobos-Grunt: Failed Russian Mars Probe Falls to Earth"] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/phobos-grunt-failed-russian-mars-probe-falls-earth/story?id=15366151 |date=20120415212921 }}. ABC News, 15 January 2012.</ref><ref name=BBCJan15>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-16491457 "Phobos-Grunt: Failed probe likely to return late Sunday"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-16491457 |date=20120828081229 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]], 15 January 2012.</ref>燃料在大气层全部烧毁，未构成危险<ref name="Sina News 2012-01-16">[http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20120117/5604059.html "俄火星探測器墜落太平洋"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20120117/5604059.html |date=20160304142828 }}. [[新浪新闻|新浪新闻]], 17 January 2012.</ref>。

